item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: admim
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.title: WELCOME
item.dc:creator: admim
item.content:encoded:
Welcome to Ashleys fashion blog!

At Ashleys fashion blog we help you style yourself as a way to say who you are without having to speak. Fashion is very important. It is life- enhancing and like everything that gives pleasure. It is worth doing it well Vivienne West-wood.

Looking more fashionable is not always about wearing the trendiest, most expensive clothes or mastering some complex styling trick. Sometimes it is as easy as just tucking in your shirt or throwing on a pair or sunglasses. So if you thinking of how you can get that it factor and have a joyfully experience with your wardrobe every day, be sure to check out our blog for killer strategies, tips and insights. Then join us today by clicking the button below to get started by learning how fashion will reflect who you are, what you feel at the moment and where you are going.

item.title: About
item.dc:creator: admim
item.content:encoded:
ABOUT

We are about helping you start about trends but also knowing who you are decide what you are, what you want to express by the way you dress and the way to live. Fashion is something we deal with every day, what we wear says a lot about ourselves especially today, when human contacts are so quick fashion is an instant language of communication. Its about making a place in the world and opening doors for yourself. Fashion is state of mind. A spirit, an extension of ones self. Fashion talks it can be an understated whisper, a high- energy scream or an all knowing wink and a smile. Most of all fashion is about being comfortable with yourself, translating self-esteem into a personal style. Ready to get started?

item.title: TITLE
item.dc:creator: admim
item.content:encoded:
3 ways to look more stylish

In order to be irreplaceable one must always be different. Coco Chanel

  1. Dont walk out the door without wearing at least one accessory:These add a bit of edge in an outfit and it can make a basic outfit remarkable.
  2. Take off those flats, and go for the heels:Shoes transform your body language and attitude. They lift you physically and emotionally. Christian Louboutin. Wearing them occasionally will have stylish benefits.
  3. Play your strengths:Whenever you are stumped about what to wear simply think of your favoritebody part, and dress to show it off.
